          <span class='member_constituency'><a href="/constituencies/middlesbrough-south-and-cleveland-east" title="Middlesbrough South and Cleveland East">(Middlesbrough, South and Cleveland, East)</a></span>
          <p class='first-para'>
            The hon. Gentleman mentioned constituents who ask how to dispose of certain
            <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_146wh' title='Col. 146WH &mdash; HC Deb 09 May 2002 vol 385 c146WH' name='column_146wh' href='#column_146wh' rel='bookmark'>146WH</a>
            products. Surely something needs to be done about individuals who do not ask that question. That is why the directive is necessary.
          </p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S6CV0385P0-03954'>
        <a name='S6CV0385P0_20020509_WH_19'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-john-taylor-1' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
