          <p class='first-para'>
            I do not think that the hon. Gentleman has given proper weight to the possibility that a number of those cars have been exported to other countries.
            
            <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_161wh' title='Col. 161WH &mdash; HC Deb 09 May 2002 vol 385 c161WH' name='column_161wh' href='#column_161wh' rel='bookmark'>161WH</a>
            When they are traded in, many cars are now exported in bulk to eastern and central Europe, where there is a market that did not really exist in 1989.
          </p>
